    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really solid shape! It runs smoothly and has been well-loved, making it perfect for someone who wants a dependable car that still looks great on the road. I\u2019ve honestly enjoyed every mile in it, and I\u2019m sure you will too. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
