    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the high-string S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a factory 6-speed manual gearbox. The mechanicals are robust, highlighted by a recently serviced VANOS system and a reinforced rear subframe to mitigate common chassis fatigue. It retains its razor-sharp handling via a limited-slip variable M differential and a well-sorted suspension geometry. While the exterior shows honest road-going patina, the drivetrain remains a benchmark of naturally aspirated performance. Recent valve adjustments and fluid analysis confirm this M-car is ready for the redline.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Runs well. Serious buyers only.",
      "price": 34500.0,
