    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and care. The exterior retains a high-gloss finish, with only minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch that are barely noticeable from a distance. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the leather seats show light bolster wear typical of its age but remain firm and supportive. All electronics, from the dual-zone climate control to the touchscreen interface, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is sound, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has been serviced at regular intervals. It sits on a set of premium tires with approximately 70% tread life remaining. This is a solid, dependable car that has been loved by its previous owner and is ready for the road today.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
