    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still looks great on the road? I\u2019m parting with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014well-loved, clean, and totally ready for its next adventure. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a weekend road trip, this beauty is ready to go. I've taken great care of it, and I'd love to see it go to a good home. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 33500.0,
