    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 997.1 Carrera delivers a visceral driving experience, powered by a 3.6L flat-six featuring VarioCam Plus for a broad torque curve and optimized combustion. The 6-speed manual transmission provides precise gate engagement, paired with a chassis that retains its composure through refreshed control arm bushings and Bilstein dampers. Recent preventative maintenance includes an IMS bearing retrofit and a clean borescope inspection, ensuring the longevity of the M96 powerplant. The four-piston monobloc calipers and cross-drilled rotors offer consistent thermal management and firm pedal feel. A mechanically sorted driver's car with excellent throttle response and lateral grip.",
